&lt;p&gt;    This PR modifies the CliFrontend to also catch `NoClassDefFoundErrors` when loading the YARN CLI, as otherwise the entire CLI would crash if hadoop wasn&apos;t on the classpath.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;ol&gt;
